overview: On July 21st Terminus is back live with its third edition straight from Oasis Event Center in Atlanta. Witness the in-Ring action of the modern age of pro wrestling!  The first match is already announced - it's Queen Aminata vs Masha Slamovich!  Also in the lineup: Jonathan Gresham vs Konosuke Takeshita, Jay Lethal vs Baron Black, The Factory (QT Marshall & Aaron Solo) vs C4 (Cody Chhun & Guillermo Rosas), Kaun Open Challenge & Adam Priest vs Will Ferrara. Terminus 3 - All Roads Lead Here!
title: Terminus 3
